15#ifndef ISC_SERIAL_H
16#define ISC_SERIAL_H 1
17
18#include <stdbool.h>
19#include <inttypes.h>
20
21#include <isc/lang.h>
22#include <isc/types.h>
23
24/*! \file isc/serial.h
25 * \brief Implement 32 bit serial space arithmetic comparison functions.
26 * Note: Undefined results are returned as false.
27 */
28
29/***
30 *** Functions
31 ***/
32
33ISC_LANG_BEGINDECLS
34
35bool
36isc_serial_lt(uint32_t a, uint32_t b);
37/*%<
38 * Return true if 'a' < 'b' otherwise false.
39 */
40
41bool
42isc_serial_gt(uint32_t a, uint32_t b);
43/*%<
44 * Return true if 'a' > 'b' otherwise false.
45 */
46
47bool
48isc_serial_le(uint32_t a, uint32_t b);
49/*%<
50 * Return true if 'a' <= 'b' otherwise false.
51 */
52
53bool
54isc_serial_ge(uint32_t a, uint32_t b);
55/*%<
56 * Return true if 'a' >= 'b' otherwise false.
57 */
58
59bool
60isc_serial_eq(uint32_t a, uint32_t b);
61/*%<
62 * Return true if 'a' == 'b' otherwise false.
63 */
64
65bool
66isc_serial_ne(uint32_t a, uint32_t b);
67/*%<
68 * Return true if 'a' != 'b' otherwise false.
69 */
70
71ISC_LANG_ENDDECLS
72
73#endif /* ISC_SERIAL_H */
